      "content": "i'll try a walking foot, thanks. but it's just so weird because it feels almost... intentional? like something is grabbing the threads from underneath for a split second and then letting go. it's really localized, like small disruptions right at the seam. any other weird mechanical stuff that causes that kind of \"tugging\" feeling?",
